      "slug": "langgraph-agents-production",
      "titulo": "Building Production-Ready AI Agents with LangGraph",
      "fecha": "2026-01-05",
      "tags": ["LangGraph", "AI Agents", "Architecture"],
      "imagen": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1677442136019-21780ecad995?w=800",
      "resumen": "Patrones de arquitectura para desplegar agentes LangGraph robustos y escalables.",
      "contenido": [
        "## De Demo a Producción",
        "",
        "Los agentes de LangGraph son potentes, pero pasar de un notebook a producción requiere considerar: estado, errores, observabilidad y escalabilidad.",
        "",
        "## Arquitectura Recomendada",
        "",
        "```",
        "┌─────────────┐     ┌─────────────┐     ┌─────────────┐",
        "│   FastAPI   │────▶│  LangGraph  │────▶│   Tools     │",
        "│   Gateway   │     │   Engine    │     │  (Sandboxed)│",
        "└─────────────┘     └─────────────┘     └─────────────┘",
        "       │                   │                   │",
        "       ▼                   ▼                   ▼",
        "┌─────────────┐     ┌─────────────┐     ┌─────────────┐",
        "│   Redis     │     │ PostgreSQL  │     │  Monitoring │",
        "│   (Cache)   │     │ (Checkpts)  │     │  (Grafana)  │",
        "└─────────────┘     └─────────────┘     └─────────────┘",
        "```",
        "",
        "## Checkpointing para Resiliencia",
        "",
        "```python",
        "from langgraph.checkpoint.postgres import PostgresSaver",
        "",
        "checkpointer = PostgresSaver.from_conn_string(",
        "    os.environ['DATABASE_URL']",
        ")",
        "",
        "graph = workflow.compile(checkpointer=checkpointer)",
        "```",
        "",
        "## Manejo de Errores",
        "",
        "```python",
        "@node",
        "def tool_executor(state: State) -> State:",
        "    try:",
        "        result = execute_tool(state.tool_call)",
        "    except ToolTimeoutError:",
        "        return state.with_error('Tool timeout')",
        "    except RateLimitError:",
        "        # Retry con backoff",
        "        raise NodeRetry(delay=60)",
        "```",
        "",
        "## Observabilidad",
        "",
        "- **LangSmith**: Trazas completas de cada ejecución",
        "- **OpenTelemetry**: Métricas y spans custom",
        "- **Prometheus**: Counters de tokens, latencia, errores",
        "",
        "## Rate Limiting",
        "",
        "```python",
        "from slowapi import Limiter",
        "",
        "limiter = Limiter(key_func=get_user_id)",
        "",
        "@app.post('/agent/invoke')",
        "@limiter.limit('10/minute')",
        "async def invoke_agent(request: AgentRequest):",
        "    ...",
        "```",
        "",
        "## Conclusión",
        "",
        "Los agentes en producción necesitan ser tratados como sistemas distribuidos: con estado persistente, manejo de fallos, y observabilidad completa."
      ]
    }
